Hi{
  "_readme": [
    "This file controls each artist's normal working days and hours.",
    "It is the ONE place to edit hours — both the website calendar and the",
    "backend booking system read from this same file, so they can never disagree.",
    "",
    "HOW TO READ/EDIT:",
    "- Each artist has their own block below: 'liz', 'yudelkys', 'johanna'.",
    "- Inside each artist's block, the keys are day-of-week numbers:",
    "    0 = Sunday, 1 = Monday, 2 = Tuesday, 3 = Wednesday,",
    "    4 = Thursday, 5 = Friday, 6 = Saturday",
    "- The value is [startHour, endHour] in 24-hour time.",
    "    Example: \"5\": [9, 19]  means Friday, 9:00 AM to 7:00 PM.",
    "- A day that is NOT listed for an artist means she does not work that day",
    "    at all — it will not appear as an option on the calendar for her.",
    "- To give someone a day off going forward, just delete that day's line.",
    "- To change hours, just change the two numbers in the brackets.",
    "- After editing, save this file and upload it to GitHub the same way",
    "    you update index.html — Netlify will redeploy automatically.",
    "- Keep this file valid JSON: every line except the last in each block",
    "    needs a comma at the end, and don't remove any commas/quotes/brackets."
  ],
